snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard speak up for Boo and Pistol
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard record a hilarious and bizarre video apologising for breaking Australia's biosecurity laws when they brought their dogs Pistol and Boo into the country. Johnny Depp gives one of the great acting performances of his life as he humbly suggests that Australians will deal with you "firmly" if you break their laws. And what of Pistol and Boo? They're safe at last. Thanks to Johnny Depp and Amber Heard.  
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard speak up for Boo and Pistol
https://youtu.be/vv-_vFyDmG0
